tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE RawDataCleaning (
    raw_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    raw_data VARCHAR(255) UNIQUE,
    cleaned_data VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL
)

CREATE TABLE data_cleaning(
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    raw_data TEXT,
    cleaned_data TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE duplicate_handling(
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    raw_data TEXT,
    cleaned_data TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE association_rule_mining(
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    rule_id INT,
    support FLOAT,
    confidence FLOAT
)
